snippet.title: Enemy of The State | Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2012040?utm_source=yttrailer

Enemy of the State is a co-op and single-player shooter set in the world of 1920s crime lords. You’re an aspiring mobster trying to reach the top during the Prohibition era. Gather your friends and perform heists all over the world. Will you build the most powerful crime syndicate in the world?
